    90	  3.0X.5  Recommendation summary
    91	  3.0X.6  Decisions for the leadership team
    92	  3.0X.7  Open questions / inputs needed
    93	```
    94	
    95	Plus a header table with: Decision density, Source coverage, KBM source path, Pivot source path.
    96	
    97	## Divergence (D-X) entry pattern
    98	
    99	Each in §3.0X.3 follows this exact structure:
   100	
   101	```
   102	### D-N. [Title — capability or design choice]
   103	
   104	**Source:** [KBM REQ-IDs from BRD with section reference]; [Pivot REQ-IDs from BRD with section reference]; [transcript references where applicable]
   105	
   106	**KBM's approach.** [Neutral description with attribution to KBM's context]
   107	
