   306	## 2.6 Implementation Approach
   307	
   308	**Advanced Receiving Tool will be deployed as a custom Orion enhancement:**
   309	- Orion Advanced Receiving Tool will be implemented for all PO receiving transactions
   310	- Tool will be accessible via web interface on both desktop and tablet
   311	- Contractors will trigger receiving workflow through Vendor Center notifications
   312	- Bin structure will be configured per location with standard naming conventions
   313	- Allocation prevention rules will be applied to damaged bins to prevent accidental selection
   314	- Integration between Vendor Center notifications and receiving workflow will be tested before go-live
   315	
   316	**Decision Points Requiring Configuration Sessions:**
   317	- Complete list of all third-party warehouse locations (drives bin setup)
   318	- Bin naming conventions (standard format for consistency)
   319	- Whether additional office/showroom bins are needed for showroom inventory or direct-to-site shipments
   320	- Receiving approval workflow (does all receiving require supervisor review, or only certain transaction types?)
