   323	
   324	## 2.7 Custom Solution Designs
   325	
   326	**REQ-002 & REQ-007 Integration: Advanced Receiving Tool with Vendor Center Notification**
   327	
   328	**Scope:** Custom Orion tool that integrates Vendor Center receiving notifications with streamlined receiving interface
   329	
   330	**High-Level Design Approach:**
   331	- Vendor Center notification triggers dashboard alert for receiving team
   332	- Advanced Receiving Tool auto-populates with PO details when receiving team selects a pending notification
   333	- Drag-and-drop interface eliminates manual NetSuite navigation
   334	- Integration with bin management system enforces allocation prevention for damaged bins
   335	- Mobile optimization ensures functionality on both tablet and desktop
   336	- Data validation ensures all received quantities match PO lines before completion
   337	
   338	**Benefits Over Standard NetSuite:**
   339	- Reduces receiving time from ~5 minutes to ~30 seconds per PO
   340	- Eliminates email dependency and communication gaps
   341	- Provides superior UX for frequent receiving transactions
   342	- Integrates notification → receiving in single workflow
   343	
   344	**Dependencies:**
   345	- Vendor Center must be configured and accessible to contractors
   346	- Bin structure must be defined before tool configuration
   347	- Mobile browser compatibility testing needed before go-live
