   670	12. Vendor issues credit memo with number (e.g., "CREDIT-12345")
   671	13. AP team creates bill credit in NetSuite with vendor's credit memo number
   672	14. VRA closed with credit status "received"
   673	
   674	**Systematic Follow-Up:**
