   682	
   683	**Result:**
   684	- Complete traceability: Damage → expected credit → actual credit received
   685	- No "lost" credits—systematic follow-up ensures collection
   686	- Vendor pressure (monthly report) encourages credit memo issuance
   687	- Financial reporting accurate because all expected credits tracked
   688	- Audit trail complete for compliance and dispute resolution
   689	
