   720	## 4.7 Custom Solution Designs
   721	
   722	**REQ-012: Monthly Expected Vendor Credits Report**
   723	
   724	**Scope:** Custom Orion report for tracking expected credits and driving collection actions
   725	
   726	**High-Level Design Approach:**
