  1215	5. Project GP reduced by 15% of labor cost (behavioral enforcement)
  1216	6. When proposal printed, line 1 is the formula line, so proposal shows line numbers starting at 2
  1217	7. Kipp hates this: "My biggest gripe about that is that it's always line one. So any time you issue a proposal with line numbers it starts at two. Somebody with OCD... I will murder this thing."
  1218	
  1219	**CURRENT WORKAROUNDS:**
