  1352	## 7.7 Custom Solution Designs
  1353	
  1354	**REQ-021, REQ-022, REQ-023: Custom 15% Labor Markup Formula Line Configuration**
  1355	
  1356	**Scope:** Custom NetSuite configuration implementing KBM Hogue's unique pricing discipline mechanism
  1357	
  1358	**High-Level Design Approach:**
  1359	- NetSuite formula line configured to calculate based on line code identification
  1360	- Line code logic: line codes starting with "EXT-" (external labor) trigger formula; all other labor codes excluded
  1361	- Formula logic: Cost = -1 × (Sum of lines where line_code matches 'EXT-%' × 0.15)
  1362	- Positioning logic: Formula line always positioned after highest line number (dynamic positioning to ensure bottom placement)
  1363	- Editability: Formula line marked as read-only and non-editable (system-level permission restriction)
  1364	- Printing logic: Formula line excluded from PDF composer templates (printing rule: exclude lines with formula line ID)
  1365	- Recalculation trigger: When labor lines added/removed/modified, formula line cost recalculates automatically
