  1371	- If order type = "Service Agreement", don't apply formula
  1372	- If customer = "BigCorp Preferred Partner", don't apply formula
  1373	- If order amount < $1,000, don't apply formula
  1374	
  1375	[Kipp to provide actual exception rules]
  1376	```
