828:## <a id="_Toc213923741"></a>3\.05 Time Tracking & Project Management
829:
830:### <a id="_Toc213923742"></a>3\.05\.01 Your Business Requirements
831:
832:Pivot Interiors requires comprehensive time tracking to measure project efficiency and prevent fraud\. Key requirements include:
833:
834:__REQ\-3\.05\.01:__ Budget vs actual reporting for design and project management work\.  Decision needed if expense records should be report against budget\.  Expensify functionality to be reviewed
835:
836:__REQ\-3\.05\.02:__ Time tracking for employees, subcontractors, and temporary resources
837:
838:__REQ\-3\.05\.03:__ Support for both full job subcontracting and supplemental labor
839:
840:__REQ\-3\.05\.04:__ Time tracking for warranty work and service revenue streams
841:
842:__REQ\-3\.05\.05:__ Integration with project margin calculations
843:
844:### <a id="_Toc213923743"></a>3\.05\.02 Current State Process
845:
846:Current time tracking is limited with no systematic budget vs actual reporting\. The organization has experienced fraud in the past with falsified time records for temporary workers\.
